verbose_text: Congruently, the BET inhibitor JQ1, which does not inhibit Erk5, suppresses Nanog without Dnmt3b induction (XREF_FIG D), indicating that XMD compounds modulate the naive primed transition via inhibition of both Erk5 and Brd4 / BET.
